	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64230660"><p><div class="quote"><p>Next is +2.0 C</p></div><p>That is unavoidable. Even if we cut CO2 emissions to zero tomorrow, the temperature would continue to climb due to the excess CO2 already in the atmosphere. The oceans add a lot of hysteresis (lag) to the process.</p><p>1.5C was never a realistic goal and neither is 2.0C.</p></div>
	</div>

